<plot>'The Pond' explores the relationship between Maisie, Tom and Joe, three children who regularly visit a pond in the village on their way home from school. For Maisie, the Pond is a place to escape her troubled home life and explore her strengthening allure to the boys, it is the place where she holds all the power over them. What she doesn't know is that the pond also holds its own deep dark secret.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?583279</url></doc>
